	<!--Long description of the mod. Single line or multi line. Supports minimal markdown subset-->
	<!--LongDescription Value="This is a long description" /-->
	<LongDescription>## Why this fix is needed

Businesses in the city do not purchase or import goods from B&amp;P DLC harbors at all. Even when the harbor has stock and is otherwise operating, buyers may still ignore it and send their trucks to other freight facilities or external road connections instead.

This breaks the expected behavior of the DLC harbor and makes it much less useful in normal city logistics.

## What this mod fixes

This mod fixes that behavior so DLC harbors can be used correctly for resource purchasing and importing.

	</LongDescription>
